<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Header with Navigation</title>
<style>
    body {
        margin: 0;
        padding: 0;
        font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
        width: 100%;
    }
    header {
        background-color: #EC715F;
        padding: 0 30px;
        box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    .header-content {
        max-width: 1024px;
        margin: 0 auto;
        display: flex;
        justify-content: space-between;
        align-items: center;
    }
    .logo img {
        width: 150px;
    }
    nav ul {
        list-style-type: none;
        display: flex;
    }
    nav ul li {
        margin-right: 30px;
    }
    nav ul li:last-child {
        margin-right: 30px;
    }
    nav ul li a {
        text-decoration: none;
        color: #fafafa;
        font-size: 16px;
    }
.main-visual {
    height: 650px;
    background-image: url('assets/mv.png');
    background-size: 100% auto;
    text-align: center;
    color: #fafafa;
}

    .main-visual h1 {
        padding-top: 200px;
        font-size: 64px;
        margin: 0;
    }
   .main-visual p {
        font-size: 20px;
    }
    main {
        width: 100%;
        background-color: #ECEFF1;
        text-align: center;
        padding-top: 90px;
        height: 100%;
    }
    main-content {
        width: 920px;
    }

    .main-content h1 {
        margin: 0;
        text-align: center;
        font-size: 32px;
        color: #000000;
        
    }
.additional-element {
    margin-left: auto;
    margin-right: auto;
    height: 3px;
    width: 70px;
    background-color: #EC715F;
    margin-top: 8px;
    margin-bottom: 30px;
}
.main-content p {
    font-size: 16px;
    width: 920px;
    margin: 0 auto; /* 中央寄せ */

}

.image-grid {
    width: 920px; /* コンテナの幅を920pxに設定 */
    height: auto; /* 高さを自動調整 */
    margin: 0 auto; /* 中央寄せ */
    padding-top: 30px;
    padding-bottom: 90px;
    display: grid;
    grid-template-columns: repeat(3, 1fr);
    grid-gap: 10px;
    justify-content: center; /* コンテナ内のアイテムを中央揃え */
}

.image-grid-item {
    width: 300px;
    height: 250px;
    overflow: hidden; /* 画像を切り抜くためにoverflowをhiddenに設定 */
}

.image-grid-item img {
    width: 100%; /* コンテナに対して100%の幅 */
    height: 100%; /* コンテナに対して100%の高さ */
    object-fit: cover; /* 画像を切り抜いてコンテナにフィットさせる */
}

</style>
</head>
<body>

<header>
    <div class="header-content">
        <div class="logo">
            <a class="navbar-brand" href="/"><img src="assets/logo.png" alt="Logo"></a>
        </div>
        <nav>
            <ul>
                <li><a href="#">Portfolio</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Feature</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Profile</a></li>
                <li><a href="#">Contact</a></li>
            </ul>
        </nav>
    </div>
</header>

<div class="main-visual">
    <div class="main-visual-content">
        <h1>Lorem Ipsum</h1>
        <p>Simply dummy text of the printing</p>
    </div>
</div>

<main>
    <div class="main-content">
        <h1>Portfolio</h1>
        <div class="additional-element"></div>
        
    <p>It islong established fact that a reader will be distracted by the readable</p>
    <p>content of a page when looking at its layout.</p>
    <p>The pointof using Lorem Ipsum is has a more-or-less norml distribution of letters</p>
        <div class="image-grid">
            <!-- Repeat the following div block 9 times for each image -->
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/websuku.png" alt="Image 1">
            </div>
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/sketch.jpg" alt="Image 2">
            </div>
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/talk.jpg" alt="Image 3">
            </div>
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/webcamp-mother.png" alt="Image 4">
            </div>
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/webcamp.png" alt="Image 5">
            </div>
            <div class="image-grid-item">
                <img src="assets/write.jpg" alt="Image 6">
            </div>
            <!-- Repeat the above div block with different image sources -->
        </div>
    </div>
</main>

</body>
</html>
